OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,FA search to set to get under way on
OL,7,FTuesday for one of the final four
OL,8,Fmembers of the Disappeared who remains
OL,9,Fmissing.
OL,11,FSeamus Maguire, 29, from Aghagallon
OL,12,Fnear Lurgan, is thought to have been
OL,13,Fkilled and secretly buried by
OL,14,Frepublican paramilitaries in 1976.
OL,16,FHis name was added to those being
OL,17,Fsearched for by the Independent
OL,18,FCommission for the Location of
OL,19,FVictims' Remains (ICLVR) in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,FHe remains missing, along with County
OL,7,FTyrone teenager Columba McVeigh,
OL,8,Fformer monk Joe Lynskey and soldier
OL,9,FRobert Nairac.
OL,11,FThe ICLVR said the search in
OL,12,FDerryclone, Co Armagh, starting on
OL,13,FTuesday will be the first for Mr
OL,14,FMaguire.
OL,16,FIt is also the first search for one of
OL,17,Fthe Disappeared in Northern Ireland
OL,18,Fsince the remains of Peter Wilson were
OL,19,Frecovered from the beach at Waterfoot,
OL,20,FCushendall, in 2010.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,FICLVR lead investigator Eamonn Henry
OL,7,Fsaid it had not been immediately clear
OL,8,Fwhether Mr Maguire was a missing
OL,9,Fperson case or the victim of an
OL,10,Fabduction, murder and secret burial by
OL,11,Fa paramilitary group.
OL,13,F"The criteria for a case to be
OL,14,Faccepted by the Commission are that
OL,15,Fthe death and secret burial was as a
OL,16,Fresult of paramilitary activity and
OL,17,Fwas carried out before the signing of
OL,18,Fthe Belfast/Good Friday Agreement on
OL,19,F10 April 1998," he said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,F"On the basis of information received
OL,7,Ffrom the PSNI, Seamus Maguire became
OL,8,Fone of the Disappeared in 2022."
OL,10,FHe said while they believe Republican
OL,11,Fparamilitaries were involved, it is
OL,12,Fnot clear which wing of the IRA was
OL,13,Fresponsible.
OL,15,FMr Henry said Mr Maguire is thought to
OL,16,Fhave been disappeared in 1976.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,F"It was initially thought that Seamus
OL,7,Fdisappeared sometime around 1973-1974
OL,8,Fbut it was also subsequently suggested
OL,9,Fthat after spending time in Manchester
OL,10,Fhe may have returned to Northern
OL,11,FIreland and was then killed and
OL,12,Fsecretly buried in the Aghagallon/
OL,13,FDerryclone area in 1976 aged 29," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"Whatever the issues around specific
OL,17,Fdates, we are now satisfied that there
OL,18,Fis sufficient credible information to
OL,19,Fcommence a search in the Derryclone
OL,20,Farea.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@aO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,F"The search area is around two acres
OL,7,Fin size and while unlike Bragan Bog
OL,8,Fwhere we searched for the remains of
OL,9,FColumba McVeigh, regrettably without
OL,10,Fsuccess, farmland is more stable each
OL,11,Fsearch site throws up its own
OL,12,Fchallenges."
OL,14,FHe said the search will continue until
OL,15,Fthey find what they are looking for or
OL,16,Fare satisfied that Mr Maguire is not
OL,17,Fthere, adding: "I'm not going to put a
OL,18,Fspecific timeframe on the search".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]yD@POUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,FMr Henry also urged anyone with
OL,7,Finformation about Mr Maguire's
OL,8,Fdisappearance to come forward.
OL,10,F"There may be an assumption that
OL,11,Fbecause a search is underway the
OL,12,FCommission has all the information we
OL,13,Fneed," he said.
OL,15,F"That is not necessarily the case.
OL,17,F"If there is anyone who has any
OL,18,Finformation on this case please get it
OL,19,Fto us.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@FO]wD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,F"All information is treated in the
OL,7,Fstrictest confidence and our sole
OL,8,Fpurpose is to return the remains of a
OL,9,Floved one to their family for a
OL,10,FChristian burial."
OL,12,FIn a statement, Mr Maguire's family
OL,13,Fdescribed him as a "much loved eldest
OL,14,Fbrother".
OL,16,F"He has been missing now for over 50
OL,17,Fyears," the family said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@RO]uD@TOUvD@HO]xD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,F"We hope that the Independent
OL,7,FCommission for the Location of
OL,8,FVictims' Remains can now recover
OL,9,FSeamus's body so that he can be buried
OL,10,Fin St Patrick's graveyard in
OL,11,FAghagallon with our parents May and
OL,12,FPatrick.
OL,14,F"Our mum looked for Seamus right up
OL,15,Funtil the day that she died.
OL,17,F"We appeal for privacy at this time.
OL,18,FOur thanks to the ICLVR and all those
OL,19,Finvolved in the search process."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland Secretary of State
OL,7,FHilary Benn said: "My thoughts are
OL,8,Ffirst and foremost with the Maguire
OL,9,Ffamily, who have endured so many years
OL,10,Fof anguish since the abduction and
OL,11,Fdisappearance of Seamus.
OL,13,F"I am deeply grateful to the
OL,14,Fcommission for their unceasing efforts
OL,15,Fto find the Disappeared and for their
OL,16,Fpainstaking efforts to help ease these
OL,17,Ffamilies' long-suffering.
OL,26,@oD@SOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779779069
OL,3,CSearch to get underway for Disappeared
OL,4,Cvictim Seamus Maguire
OL,6,F"As well as the Maguire family, the
OL,7,Ffamilies of Columba McVeigh, Joseph
OL,8,FLynskey and Robert Nairac still await
OL,9,Fthe return of their loved ones'
OL,10,Fremains.
OL,12,F"I urge anyone with information ` no
OL,13,Fmatter how insignificant they think it
OL,14,Fmay be ` to come forward and speak to
OL,15,Fthe commission. All information will
OL,16,Fbe treated in the strictest
OL,17,Fconfidence."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/11
